Package org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core

Class QueryDSLAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core.QueryDSLAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ForeignAdapter<com.querydsl.core.types.Expression<?>>
    @API(status=EXPERIMENTAL,
     since="2021.1.0")
public final class QueryDSLAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ForeignAdapter<com.querydsl.core.types.Expression<?>>
    This is a utility class to turn a several Query-DSL expressions into something the Cypher-DSL can understand. It can only be used when `com.querydsl:querydsl-core` is on the classpath. While we try our best to translate as many expression as possible into syntactically correct Cypher, we don't provide any guarantees that the expressions and conditions generated are semantically correct in the context of the final query generated.
    Since:
    2021.1.0
    Author:
    Michael J. Simons
